<OUTPUT_TEXT>
To: [Designated Department/Team Name]  
From: Customer Service Department  
Date: [Today's Date]  
Subject: Referral of Unresolved Customer Grievances for Further Investigation

Dear Team,

We are forwarding a set of unresolved customer grievances that require your specialized review and further investigation. Despite our initial efforts to address these concerns, resolution was not achieved at the customer service level.

Please find attached a summary of each case, including relevant correspondence and documentation. We kindly request your prompt attention to these matters and an update on the progress or resolution status at your earliest convenience.

Thank you for your cooperation.

Best regards,  
[Your Name]  
Senior Customer Service Representative  
[Your Contact Information]
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
